== INSTALL

=== Prerequisites

* <<Ruby>> 1.8.6 or newer.

* <<RubyGems>> 1.3.6 or newer.

=== Installing

Installing as a <<Ruby>> library:

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
gem install ember
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Installing as a <<Rails>> plugin:

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
script/plugin install <%= @code_repo_url.sub('http', 'git') %>.git
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Upgrading

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
gem update ember
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Removing

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
gem uninstall ember
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
